	   <tr><td colspan=2>Use the best weapon for the best situaltion<br><br>Bash can be use to interupt spells. This is critical at higher levels. So when fighting mobs that cast spells use 1hs and bash. Spell casters have less hp anyway, so if your dmg goes down a little it's no biggy. And when fighting melee mobs switch over to 2hs. Most 2hs weapons do more damage then 1hs weapons; so 2hs works better on mobs with more hp<br>just a thought<br>Rastamon of Cazic Thule<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
