	   <tr><td colspan=2>Blacksmithing is the way to go if you want a killer amount of cash at early levels.&nbsp;&nbsp;I am a level 12 pally and now my skill in blacksmithing is at Master-Smith, which is beyond 101.  I dumped all my cash into smithing since level 2.  And although you won't have a realy good weapon or armor in the begining, once you have started making Banded Armor pieces (65 smith-skill) you will gain it all back and more.  I am now at skill level 130 and I can make all banded armor items.  I have also earned enough cash to purchase some great armor and weapons, my personal favorite I've purchased being a Ghoulbane.   Banded is really cheap to make and sells quite well to players level 1-20.  Now I have over 500pp in the bank, and I've learned a skill that is very much admirable.  Good luck,<br><br>Tenniel<br>13th Paladin of Rodcet Nife server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
