	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would like to get a few ideas on how I can make my Paladin a little more effective.&nbsp;&nbsp;At the moment I am 13Lvl in FP.  I have decided to take a trip to Crushbone since everyone is telling me how great the wealth is from hunting.  Right now, I currently have a Wraith Bone Hammer and a small round shield.  My 1HB skill is great because I have been using 1HBs since my piece of wood I've gotten at level one.  Here is my concern.  My WB Hammer hits from 7-18 but my shield bashes for only 1-8.  Would it be better for me to buy a better shield? And if so, what should I buy since I only have 75pp to my name.  Or should I invest in a 2HS? (don't think I would have bash anymore) Or should I get another shield and aquire a 1HS weapon?  How is the dmg determined on a shield?  By AC?  All this talk about Ghoulbane is great if you have over 1Kpp to buy one.  Thanks.  And another thing, about shields, I am going to Crushbone to hunt for a shiny brass shield.  Does this do good damage?<br><br>Tenniel<br>13th Paladin of the Rocet Nife server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
